# Security Policy — {{ repoName }}

## Supported Versions

| Version | Supported |
| ------- | --------- |
| latest  | ✅ |

## Reporting a Vulnerability

Please report security vulnerabilities by:

1. **Do not** open a public GitHub issue
2. Email {% if maintainerEmail %}{{ maintainerEmail }}{% else %}the maintainers{% endif %} with subject: `[SECURITY] {{ repoName }}`
3. Include a description and reproduction steps

We will respond within 72 hours and issue a patch within 7 days for critical issues.

## Security Scanning

This project uses `cargo audit` for automated dependency vulnerability scanning.
See [.github/workflows/audit.yml](.github/workflows/audit.yml).
